title: Flower Travellin Band - Pussies to death 10000 yr freakout
description:
This is the rarest of the Flower Travellin' Band discography (Misspelled as Flower Traveling Band on front cover). A very limited vinyl only release from 1995. It is 1969-70 studio outtakes from Yuya Uchida & The Flowers album "Challenge" before they became the Flower Travellin' Band.  From Pussies to Death in 10,000 Years of Freak Out! These were crazy sides recorded before the golden dawn of the Flower Travelling Band. Extreme suites of lead-molten guitar, poured with pain and beautiful psychedelic wonder into the mouth of the round eye cow.

FROM PUSSIES TO DEATH IN 10,000 YEARS OF FREAKOUT (recorded '69-'70) released(1995)
